</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='filter' href='#filter'></a> filter</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Filter to apply</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p><code>*</code></p>
</p></dd></dl>
</div>
